1. U Sjedinjenim Državama potroši se *milijarde* dolara godišnje na vojsku. (*milijarde* - billions) (In the United States, billions of dollars are spent annually on the military.)

2. Njihova kompanija ostvaruje *milijarde* prihoda svake godine. (*milijarde* - billions) (Their company generates billions in revenue every year.)

3. Zemlja se suočava sa *milijardama* dolara štete nakon prirodne katastrofe. (*milijardama* - billions) (The country is facing billions of dollars in damage after a natural disaster.)

4. Vlada je donela odluku da uloži *milijardu* dinara u zdravstvo. (*milijardu* - billion) (The government has decided to invest a billion dinars in healthcare.)

5. Grad će izdvojiti *milijardu* dinara za obnovu infrastrukture. (*milijardu* - billion) (The city will allocate a billion dinars for infrastructure reconstruction.)

6. Kompanija je kupila novu opremu za *milijardu* dinara. (*milijardu* - billion) (The company bought new equipment for a billion dinars.)

7. Oni su uspeli da sakupljaju *milijardu* dinara za dobrotvorne svrhe. (*milijardu* - billion) (They managed to raise a billion dinars for charity purposes.)

8. Uložili su *milijardu* evra u projekat izgradnje novog aerodroma. (*milijardu* - billion) (They invested a billion euros in the project to build a new airport.)

9. Prošle godine, potrošili su *milijardu* litara goriva u Srbiji. (*milijardu* - billion) (Last year, they consumed a billion liters of fuel in Serbia.)

10. Nacionalni dug zemlje premašuje *milijarde* dolara. (*milijarde* - billions) (The country's national debt exceeds billions of dollars.)